To run notewise:

  Checkout from svn:

    svn co https://notewise.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ notewise

  Build:
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    
  Create a new mysql database:

    mysql -uroot -p -e 'create database notewise'

  Import the database schema:

    mysql -uroot -p notewise < createTablesMySql.sql

  Create a test user and starting kernel:
    ./create_user.pl

  Copy config-sample.yml to config.yml and edit as appropriate.

          set Static to 1
          set Debug to 1
          set BaseUrl to /

  Run 'script/notewise_server.pl -k -r' to test the application.  The default port number is 3000.  To change the port number, use 'script/notewise_server.pl -k -r -p 3005'.


To run the command line unit tests, do:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make test
